<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
  <head>
    <meta content="text/html; charset=UTF-8" http-equiv="Content-Type" />
    <style>
      body {
        font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
        color: #333;
        margin: 0;
        padding: 20px;
      }
      .container {
        max-width: 600px;
        background: #ffffff;
        padding: 20px;
        margin: auto;
        border-radius: 8px;
        box-shadow: 0px 0px 10px rgba(255, 193, 7, 0.5);
        border-left: 5px solid #ffc107;
      }
      h1 {
        color: #ffc107;
        font-size: 20px;
      }
      p {
        font-size: 14px;
        line-height: 1.6;
      }
      table {
        width: 100%;
        border-collapse: collapse;
        margin-top: 15px;
      }
      th, td {
        border: 1px solid #ddd;
        padding: 10px;
        text-align: left;
      }
      th {
        background: #ffc107;
        color: white;
        font-weight: bold;
      }
      tr:nth-child(even) {
        background-color: #f9f9f9;
      }
      a {
        color: #ffc107;
        text-decoration: none;
        font-weight: bold;
      }
      .footer {
        font-size: 12px;
        color: #777;
        text-align: center;
        margin-top: 20px;
      }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <div class="container">
      <h1>Notification: Low NPIDs at <%= @site_details[:location_name] %></h1>

      <p>
        Attention: <%= @site_details[:location_name] %> is running low on NPIDs. 
        At the current consumption rate, the remaining NPIDs are expected to be depleted in 
        <strong><%= @site_details[:days_remaining].round %></strong> days.
      </p>

      <p><strong>Current Status:</strong></p>

      <table>
        <tr>
          <th>Parameter</th>
          <th>Value</th>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td>Unassigned NPIDs</td>
          <td><%= @site_details[:unassigned] %></td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td>Average Consumption (Per Day)</td>
          <td><%= @site_details[:avg_consumption_rate_per_day].round %></td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td>Estimated Days Remaining</td>
          <td><%= @site_details[:days_remaining].round %></td>
        </tr>
      </table>

      <p>
        Please take the necessary steps to replenish the NPIDs. 
        For more details, visit: 
        <a href="https://ddedashboard.hismalawi.org" target="_blank">DDE Dashboard</a>.
      </p>

      <p>Thank you,</p>
      <p><strong>Demographics Data Exchange</strong></p>

      <div class="footer">
        &copy; <%= Time.now.year %> Demographics Data Exchange. All rights reserved.
      </div>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>
